Improvements to image sharing. In this new version you can send images in your private chats. For additional privacy these images cannot be saved by those who receive them and will automatically expire after 1 day! Images you share can be deleted at any time. After expiring or being deleted images will no longer be available and will be deleted from the servers. An In App purchase allows you to select other durations for these images. Would you like to see new features Email us at info lext talk.com

We have redesigned Lext Talk to give you a greater experience. We have also worked hard in fixing most of the bugs you reported and making things faster and nicer. We hope you enjoy it!

Welcome to the new Lext Talk with some new cool features: Landscape mode for an easier chat control and nicer map display. The app is now available in English Spanish Catalan and French. More available languages to chat and translate Public chat rooms by language so you can practice a language with many people at a time New United Nations flag to represent other languages not supported by the translation service The chat rooms now show the number of users and messages
